The exactr package as a whole is distributed under LGPL-3.0-only.  The exactr package includes adaptations of components from other open source software projects.  The following is a list of these projects:

* Boost C++ Libraries: BSL-1.0
* plink2: written by package author
* R: GPL-2.0-or-later
* QD library: BSD-3-Clause-LBNL
